        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This method may be called on the receiver to convert device-independent chromaticity values to device-specific RGB white balance gain values."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "This method throws an "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsinvalidargumentexception"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " exception if any of the "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "chromaticityValues"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " fields are set outside the range "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "[0,1]"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Some "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "chromaticityValues"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " field combinations yield out-of-range device RGB values that will cause an exception to be thrown if passed directly to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice/1624568-setwhitebalancemodelockedwithdev"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ".  Be sure to verify that red, green, and blue gain values are within the range of ["
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "1.0"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " - "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
